# Code Verification & Assertion Specs
- All metric extraction utilities must be accompanied by explicit test blocks or runtime assertions.
- Every mathematical function must test bounds constraints (e.g., handling negative values, zero, or null arrays).
- Include inline assertions checking that file pathways are valid before attempts to execute static analysis.




